{"type": "article", "id": 56603, "title": "传私募基金有意收购 Pandora，以及，米兰时装周开幕 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-09-20T09:09:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 239, "name": "米兰时装周"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180920170715vOiplhaVNtk1EbIn.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-09-18/pandora-soars-after-report-that-pe-funds-may-buy-jewelry-maker\" rel=\"nofollow\">传私募基金有意收购 Pandora，公司股价飙升 11%&nbsp;</a></strong>| 丹麦珠宝品牌 Pandora 的股价与 2016 年 5 月高峰时期相比已下滑了 60%，市值也由当年的 180 亿美元下滑至如今的 70 亿美元。意大利《24 小时太阳报》（Il Sole 24 Ore）报道称，KKR 集团和贝恩资本等私募股权基金有收购意向，Pandora 股价随后于周二上涨了 11%。不过，Pandora 和&nbsp;KKR 集团等均拒绝做出回应。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.engadget.com/2018/09/19/amazon-scout/\" rel=\"nofollow\">亚马逊测试新功能 Scount，通过点“赞”或“踩”推荐购物</a></strong> | 不同于以往根据用户的浏览记录或已购买物品进行推荐，Scount 功能会先向用户展示一系列产品图片，根据用户反应做出相应推荐。目前这一功能主要覆盖家居家具这一类别。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://weibo.com/2591168064/GA8ewvOxy?from=page_1006062591168064_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime&amp;type=comment\" rel=\"nofollow\">意大利奢侈男装品牌 Ermenegildo Zegna 宣布陈伟霆和吴世勋为全球形象代言人</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 品牌官方微博于 9 月 20 日凌晨宣布了这一消息，并在同一条微博中附上了中国限定 XXX 系列运动衫的官网购买链接。Ermenegildo Zegna 于 1991 年进入中国，目前这里已成为该品牌全球最大市场。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.bbtnews.com.cn/2018/0919/266952.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\">Esprit 母公司去年亏损 25 亿港元，销售点减少 555 个</a>&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;Esprit 母公司思捷环球发布截至 2018 年 6 月 30 日的年度财报显示，期内实现收入 154.55 亿港元，同比下降 3.05%；毛利 79.21 亿港元，同比下跌 3.75%；股东应占溢利由盈转亏，亏损达到 25.54 亿港元，比去年同期的 6700 万港元下跌 3911.94%。期内，思捷环球还出售了两间物业附属公司。上一财年，思捷环球曾提出关于品牌年轻化、产品升级、新一代渠道、市场规模优化和降低成本的战略，迄今为止尚未有明显成效。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong>Louis Vuitton 推出第九款香水“Attrape-Rêves”，寓意“追梦者”。</strong>配料中使用了非洲可可花、芍药、广藿香、土耳其玫瑰、佛手柑和姜。</p><p>Emma Stone 为其拍摄了一组广告大片，并出演了 LV 有史以来的第一支香水推广影片，由 Sam Mendes 导演。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920160232EbUB5vq2PQwYm9XO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=v0710dembbg\"></iframe> </figure>  </div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.anothermag.com/art-photography/11179/paris-women-artists-photographed-in-the-intimacy-of-their-studios\" rel=\"nofollow\">法国摄影师 Vincent Ferrané 的新影像系列“Visitor”</a></strong>，在巴黎 17 位年轻女性艺术家的工作室里拍摄了她们日常工作的样子。<br></p><p>这些影像已集结成书，将于 9 月 22 日由&nbsp;Libraryman 出版社出版。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809201520442IoYzUNKlZJ5xvMb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152041CZ5KQcGwnodJBAWH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152042GhHSuoWr0LZjltJ1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809201520427gjen1YFaGiUKhmy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.514844\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152048LsUHGmqzpe3JAbgN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152043EudQ8aCiXSmFz2re.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.514844\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152042D14ioJdbCSeXzFh6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152046ZpE9RbiYJ7P34Ag1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809201520467aDAkJPRBCuFMHXU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152046CaLW4TytRuXhorsK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152047xpGR5W2tIvUdShTj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.521628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152048d5ZCp4DUJGnqe90b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.514844\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152151CsWXhqTBSrn7kmvl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152152u3KsQBUN0cHxTIO1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152149GsVDuypBE8CNF4rh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152149hsp7r0FDWHzVNlfA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920152151NZ3mf148OzWSJpFU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809201521521rtyv5kFbleNTo6q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>米兰时装周于 9 月 19 日开幕。</strong><br></p><p><strong>Jill Sander 2019 春季成衣系列：</strong></p><p>发布会在一个原本用来生产圣诞节蛋糕的厂房里举行。新系列延续了创始人极简、严肃的廓形，色调也仍以浅色系为主，但在细节上加入了一些俏皮的元素。比如胸口的手绘线条画，实用的大口袋，带拉链的宽肩背心，沙漏型、镶有层层褶皱的连衣长裙等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150820aHQKsV7BYIAUJXGl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150806JGlXFTcw6Wt02PDB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150806cqsjTJK9GfuemUo4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809201508069XvTEkQPH5wgf2U1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150807OtHhgXJApzKUq8fD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150807pMU0Va129toNxkCE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150807hETWgkvwyJ4e3lj8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150807R5nZ2NQAwGYCW3gq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150808gtb0G7mUl46op9jh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150808HvNO5LKaYuwtVxBi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150808JgQ8s4hmGfH7ARN9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150809pNmBScs2UA1Y5d8L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150809CMUWuZLRQkm20nOs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150809BSMPlxH1jECbf8K0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150809gt8z3SC9lUILcwEu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150810fHoT78e0gWXntJVK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150810Q9DhgA5qp6FSPWjU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150811Hht7GsemEUCwj4XK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150811Q6TAMBDacWIp23F1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150812JWXmxU1YOwhgb54s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150813dfx5kPgZRnXO1B8I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150814dQNk0bJVLg2fPAlB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150815xjwumWL4ovsXg061.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150815b8qRLhl0GNgXcyQa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150816Uut6y5Mj0gvmAInW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150816NObnh3ZfPI0A26yE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150817UaKMoO6wPjS0tDgy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150817jFy4rDpMJhCVmeXi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920150818vzyc04XtKLubAqrO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809201508199c1kjNenyD5V0JRa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>N°21 2019 春季成衣系列：</strong></p><p>N°21 是意大利设计师 Alessandro Dell’Acqua 8 年前成立的新品牌，那时他已 48 岁。此前，他先后出任过意大利奢侈品牌 Pietro Pianforini 和高级羊绒品牌 Malo 的创意总监，也经历过同名品牌被卖后发展不顺的挫折。</p><p>N°21 算是他东山再起的一次尝试，也为他之后担任法国老牌 Rochas 的创意总监铺平了道路。今年 5 月 10 日，N°21 刚于北京三里屯太古里开出中国首家旗舰店。</p><p>新系列算是过往系列中额外装饰和印花使用得最少的一季，只有少数几条裙子饰有鲜艳的鸵鸟毛，大部分则依靠剪裁以及面料本身的光泽制造性感的氛围。Tod's CEO&nbsp;Diego Della Valle 坐在了前排，表示双方有可能合作推出一个联名系列。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151132lyLo7vCXUrD56xEg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151133xPHuo5DpF4Yrhenl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151133D5RTdv3GAN6sCI7b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151134RaPX5rMO7xeF9LEy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151134kNm6C7uYiwEKs1QI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151135107dqsE9WOiulM6V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151135gfEJAhxMmkKX4dIa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018092015113638SBk5mDCFOG6dTy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809201511351g34ik0aNvRP87Br.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151136NGDSYM7OW8Zvewkc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151137bdOY1oCmwaVI3uEh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151137dp7lsbNyAYUj3gPV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151137Ohk0eNJYgTCU6PKn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151138wuv4EgFWAQM0tCSG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151138nQmIYdfCRqhwMoki.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151138oLrEwqOavj6F4Ye9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151139b3t1ORaYj5fkLw07.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151251IFR8Wtmy37MHVag2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>Annakiki 2019 春季成衣系列：</strong></p><p>中国设计师&nbsp;Anna Yang 在国内的知名度一般，但由于为 Beyoncé 之女 Blue Ivy 出席&nbsp;Wearable Art Gala&nbsp;晚会以及英国歌手&nbsp;Ebony Bones 专辑封面造型制衣，Annakiki 在欧洲积累起了一定名气。&nbsp;</p><p>本季主题为“Fashion Glitch”（直译“时尚脉冲”），将设计师对于电子乐的喜爱和夜店年轻人爱穿的闪光面料和霓虹色调结合起来。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151514VDFQJ5zt3BMmWHIh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151400LD6wxurb7UYqcogv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151359ODGnjq8HEKeXucyC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151359nYIXHDUOlPamqF2g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151400h9jS6uClFvxsKEtJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151401LP0FtQmdyDxnK57W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151401U41nmTo5zCE0Kjsy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151401IdOzo0ya8xuPtCf9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151402jcTQqgbDadUIRX8k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151403KDVmaZqnWfgNs2j5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151403xZt3H827dS4NwirE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151403JwyXMWbVxzhgeORn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151403DvK6PuLdI9B74rto.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151404KvVQqeWL0rkaliTz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151404vlcbLdjD0wyCUr6k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151405hdnfACVQkiYclsUP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151405dwBtjnF9WLIZSVzr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151406PjDCgbWl2iRSG94J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809201514063bwPZnQsV82BpkzW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151409kb7dmu46vXRHBa0L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809201514109fzuo1A0SPZYFTK4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151411em04UZBISpQ3qoYa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151412i9ZBX2encPqAy6pD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151408sPGa9t25f6dLIDrR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809201514144PpoyZ5JCbVh2dtI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920151414glbuercYPKCFytxv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图为&nbsp;Vincent Ferrané&nbsp;作品</p>"}